import React from 'react'
import { Card, Col, Row } from 'react-bootstrap'

const Cardlist = () => {
    return (
    <Row>
        <Col>
                <Card sm="12" className='mb-3'>
            <Card.Img className='img-' style={{width:"50px"}} variant="top" src="02.jpg" />
            <Card.Body>
            <Card.Title>وجبه فطار</Card.Title>
            <Card.Text>
                وصف وجبه الفطار للبطل
            </Card.Text>
            </Card.Body>
            </Card>
            </Col>
    </Row>
    )
}

export default Cardlist
